Very perverse pleasure to be found around taking delight in belonging to two different spheres of life. "I am a poet and philosopher but hang out with my ghetto friends!" "I am a reactionary but on occasion do drugs and am cool!" You can always hear the giddiness at the duality.

For leftists types it's usually about 4chan humor, the more a group enforces a moral hygiene the greater the pleasure of breaking it. We all do this, every single one, it's an impulse to show how cool you are. Hemingway enjoying his performative masculinity in literature circles.
